beer.beer_description: Young Henrys Hazy is pure goodness! Pouring a delish golden pale, with a gorgeous off white head, this beer is a wonder to behold! A pungent bouquet of tropical stone fruit and citrus wafts through the air, making way for a pillowy, perfectly balanced mouthfeel and flavour. New to the core range in both keg and can, it's ready to be thoroughly enjoyed by all!
